com.azure.data.cosmos.internal.changefeed

Interface Lease

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ServiceItemLease

    public interface Lease
    Represents a lease that is persisted as a document in the lease collection.

    Leases are used to: Keep track of the ChangeFeedProcessor progress for a particular Partition Key RANGE. Distribute load between different instances of ChangeFeedProcessor. Ensure reliable recovery for cases when an instance of ChangeFeedProcessor gets disconnected, hangs or crashes.
